snippet.title: DazzlingKate22
snippet.description: Hey there I'm DazzlingKate! I'm an artist, a nerd, and a dog mom to 2 lovely poochies. I'm very excited to be here on youtube for positive videos here, the nerdy news and I spend my weekends on streams for games I play. I hope you and I can be amazing friends and let's nerd out together! :D
